  "texts": [
    "Plant defense research encompasses various \"omics\" technologies, each offering unique insights into the molecular mechanisms underlying plant responses to pathogens and environmental stresses.",
    "In the following sections, we'll provide a brief overview of the primary types of data each omics approach can provide when applied to research on plant stress.",
    "Plants, as stationary organisms, have evolved sophisticated defense mechanisms against various stressors, including biotic and abiotic factors.",
    "The combination of genomics and AI has become a potent tool for unraveling the genetic foundations of plant defense.",
    "This review explores the current and future applications of AIassisted genomics in understanding both biotic and abiotic stress responses in plants."
  ],
